      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary vehicle that balances refined performance with documented care. This specimen has been maintained to a high standard, showcasing a pristine interior and a robust powertrain that ensures a confident driving experience. Having passed our comprehensive multi-point inspection, it represents a premier acquisition for the discerning professional seeking both prestige and proven durability. Experience the intersection of sophisticated engineering and enduring value.",
      "price": 36500.0,
